Package com.rift.coad.lib.naming.cos

Class Summary
CosContext This object wrapps the complexity of speaking to the Cos Naming Server.
CosNamingContextManager This class is responsible for managing the naming naming context.
javaURLContextFactory This object is responsible for instanciating URL context objects on demand.
MasterContext This is the master context responsible for managing both the URL in memory contexts and the Cos contexts.
MemoryContext This is an in memory version of a context object.
MemoryNamingEnumeration This object implements the Naming enumeration for the memory context.
NamingParser This object is responsible for parsing the string value passed in.
URLContext This object is responsible for implementing the JNDI context within Coadunation.
URLInitialContextFactory The object responsible for constructing the initial context factory.
 

Exception Summary
CosNamingException This exception is thrown by the cos naming manager.
